00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,640
=Just Wanna Be With You=

10
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,360
(Adapted From
Zhihu Novelist, Little Qi's)

11
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,260
("Three Marriages
to the Underworld Lord")

12
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:10,260
=Episode 9=

13
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,920
Isn't this the forbidden land
of Cangyun?

14
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,200
Why did you bring me here?

15
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:29,959
And...

16
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,959
You don't fare well in the cold.

17
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,280
You're right.

18
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:35,760
I don't.

19
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:38,840
But with you,

20
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,120
