and weakened your cultivation.

24
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,519
You gave up so much for me.

25
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,600
Have you really forgotten all of it?

26
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,480
Who are you?

27
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,599
I'm your beloved,

28
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,599
Jiang Jinghuai.

29
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,560
That name...

30
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,639
You're the one who gave me that name.

31
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:25,719
You named me Jiang Jinghuai.

32
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,159
Me?

33
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,039
And you're the one

34
