35
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:36,800
only true love can make
the Silver Snow Flower bloom.

36
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,319
Look.

37
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,039
Do you remember now?

38
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,520
I...

39
