(The air in my face,
the scent of the flowers,)

43
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,000
(everything!)

44
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,240
(I want to give you
this sense of freedom.)

45
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,160
(Do you like it?)

46
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,160
I do.

47
00:04:33,381 --> 00:04:37,229
♪The low moon weighs down my weary brow♪

48
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:40,920
(May our hearts beat as one,)

49
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:45,040
(faithful and true in love.)

50
00:04:47,672 --> 00:04:50,472
♪Like snow falling across the sky♪

51
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:53,160
Jiang Jinghuai.

52
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,560
Jiang Zhiyu.

53
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,000
Jiang Jinghuai.

54
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,000
(I have a new name.)

55
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,639
(That makes me happy.)

56
00:05:01,403 --> 00:05:05,258
♪I fear time turning to ash in a blink♪

57
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,160
(The foxfolk)

58
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,600
(only adorn a girl with flowers
if they truly love her.)

59
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,000
(If flowers are worn in this life,
beauty follows in the next.)

60
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:13,400
