I love him. I want to marry him!

64
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,959
I want to marry him!

65
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,000
(She must make her wedding vows)

66
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,199
(with me, Jiang Jinghuai.)

67
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:31,199
(I, Jiang Jinghuai, swear,)

68
00:05:31,767 --> 00:05:33,000
(by the Silver Snow Flower,)

69
00:05:33,781 --> 00:05:35,190
(that I will love only Jiang Zhiyu.)

70
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,279
Huai!

71
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,800
(In this life and every life to come.)

72
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:39,959
(I want to marry you.)

73
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,079
(Will you marry me?)

74
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,399
(I will.)

75
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:44,399
Huai...

76
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,399
Huai...

77
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,800
You're my Huai.

78
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,839
How could I ever forget you?

79
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,199
I'm sorry.

80
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,839
You remember everything now?

